      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Although this is probably clearer as an example, you could also write <code>if(value!=null || map.containsKey(key))</code> for the second part.  At least if you want to do the same thing either way -- no repeated code.  It&#39;ll work due to <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Short-circuit_evaluation\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">short circuiting</a>."
    } ],
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 11683,
      "reputation" : 1520502,
      "user_id" : 22656,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 86,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/6d8ebb117e8d83d74ea95fbdd0f87e13?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "Jon Skeet",
